Package: bojapi
Title: Access the Bank of Japan Time-Series Data API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kenji", "Miyazaki", email = "kenjimyzk@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An unofficial, tidy, rate-limited interface to the 'Bank of Japan
    Time-Series Data Search' API. Search series metadata, retrieve observations
    by series code or hierarchy, follow pagination automatically, and work with
    normalized long or wide data frames. The API does not require an API key.
URL: https://github.com/kenjimyzk/bojapi
BugReports: https://github.com/kenjimyzk/bojapi/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.1.0),
    tibble
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
